properties.description: Array containing all data properties of API output.

id.description: Object with information about the data.

geo_type.description: Type of geography of output data. If not specified, API returns best available.

geo_zoom.description: Maximum zoom level using Web Mercator tile system.

geo_id.description: Unique identifier of geography within geo_type.

value.description: Object containing output values of aggregated data.

total.description: Output values for total aggregated data.

weekday.description: Output values for data on weekdays: Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, and Friday.

weekend.description: Output values for data on weekend: Saturday and Sunday

onpeak.description: Output values during on peak times: Weekdays (7:00am - 10:00am and 4:00pm - 8:00pm).

offpeak.description: Output values during off peak times: Weekdays (before 7:00am, 10:00am - 4:00pm, after 8:00pm) and Weekends.

hourly.description: Object containing individual hourly data using 24 hour clock: hours 0 - 23.

hour_{0-23}.description: Output values for data of specific hour of the day. Includes all days of the week.

download.description: Aggregated download speed values. Measured in megabytes per second (mbps).

upload.description: Aggregated upload speed values. Measured in megabytes per second (mbps)

latency.description: Aggregated upload speed values. Measured in milliseconds (ms)

packet_loss.description: Aggregated packet loss values. Measured in percentage (%)

participation.description: Number of test participants included in the aggregated data.

median.description: The value of the middle of the range of aggregated data.

average.description: The mean or average value of the aggregated data.

max.description: The maximum or highest value of the aggregated data.

min.description: The minimum or lowest value of the aggregated data.

bbox.description: Numeric array of the bounding box of the minimum/maximum latitude/longitude of the geography.

geometry.description: Object containing the geographic information of the aggregated data.

coordinates.description: Numeric array of geographic WGS84 latitude/longitude coordinate pairs.

bins.description: Number of binned groups of data. Includes total plus specific geographies.

aggregations.description: Number of aggregated results. Includes total plus specific geographies and carriers.
